<div class="tag">
<a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e8%af%97%e7%bb%8f">诗经</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e9%97%ba%e6%80%a8">闺怨</a>
